{
  "stem": "21817.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we can, we can start living like a human being, even the conditions were very bad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was not sufficient food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were no, no showers or toilets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That, that was a given that you go just in the woods.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, they started already-- they had already some food over there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "What they used to do before I arrived, they had some food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then I find out what they do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "At night, they used to have a group of men with guns already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They had guns, but not enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I tried to learn how to use a gun.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They showed us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And from time to time, we used to go on patrol.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we had to know how to use, how to use a gun.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we used to go to the farms, you know, the farmers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In that area, people use a lot of potatoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In the wintertime, they used to make big stacks of potatoes, put straw on top, and then dirt.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This protects it from freezing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We knew about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So we had-- we had-- in the camp, we had some cows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We had some horses and sled, sled.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we used to go over there and actually steal it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We open up one corner, take out as much potato we can, and cover it up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They knew about it, the farmers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But they had no control over it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They were afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were afraid for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They were afraid of the partisan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Because if they do-- tell the local militia or the Germans-- there used to be always a combination between Germans and, and, and the local, local militia.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Used to be one or two Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The rest of them were all local people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They were serving with the German army.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
